{"type": "article", "id": 2857, "title": "Vans Classics 2014 假日 Tobacco系列鞋", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-15T08:09:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232303eNbi6YxP4H5yz7wZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tVans 近日发布了 「Classics 2014 假日 Tobacco」系列鞋款，顾名思义，此系列以 Tobacco 为设计灵感，三款 Era、Old Skool、Half Cab 鞋型全部采用烟草棕色，并搭配橡胶大底，使得鞋身与鞋底浑然一体。值得一提的是，此番设计分别运用了麂皮与牛巴革材质，在凸显质感的同时，且非常适用于在气温降低的秋冬季穿着。Era、Old Skool、Half Cab 三款鞋型分别售价为 55 美元、60 美元和 65 美元，<a href=\"http://www.vans.com/shop/CategoryDisplay?urlRequestType=Base&amp;catalogId=10703&amp;categoryId=1010147&amp;pageView=image&amp;beginIndex=0&amp;langId=-12&amp;top_category=1091105&amp;parent_category_rn=1091108&amp;storeId=10154\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232300eWGwrVcY1nTvjMpR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232301iosKClN8dzRbj2cM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232301tUCDcLkSyZz0bWRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052323023f9V0b8DWJGOBXN1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}